-- Infosys Americas Banking Head Farooq Said to Quit to Join Wipro
-- B y   K e t a k i   G o k h a l e
-- 2012-09-03T11:58:42Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-03/infosys-americas-banking-head-farooq-said-to-quit-to-join-wipro.html
Infosys Ltd. (INFO) ’s head of financial
services in the U.S., the company’s largest services segment,
resigned and will join competitor  Wipro Ltd. (WPRO) , said a Wipro
official who declined to be identified ahead of an announcement.  Shaji Farooq served nearly 11 years as the head of
Infosys’s Financial Services Americas unit, according to his
LinkedIn profile.  North America  contributed 65.1 percent of Infosys’s revenue
in the year ended March, and banking and financial services
contributed 27.9 percent of revenue that year, according to a
fact sheet from the company.  To contact the reporter on this story:
